creator: TrainerPlan
descriptionHtml: This app is the athlete's companion app for TrainerPlan (trainerplan.co). If your coach uses it you can receive your workouts through your mobile phone instantly.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: New smileys for when you mark your workouts as complete

title: TrainerPlan for Athletes

creator: TrainerPlan
descriptionHtml:
With TrainerPlan, athletes can instantly see all the activities added by their coaches and coaches can keep in touch with their athletes and add events, trainings, etc.

Receive notifications directly on your mobile when you have a new training, event or comments from your coach and / or athlete.
descriptionShort: The simplest way to manage your athletes

title: TrainerPlan

creator: TrainerPlan
descriptionHtml:
Transform your training with TrainerPlan! A dynamic platform where coaches and athletes connect to achieve extraordinary goals.

Athletes can instantly discover and follow personalized plans and activities designed by their coach.

Coaches can manage and track the progress of their athletes, adding workouts, events, and real-time feedback. Communication is seamless and effective with instant notifications for every new workout, event, or message.

Maximize your performance and achieve your objectives with TrainerPlan, where every training session counts!
descriptionShort: Connect and empower training between athletes and coaches
